'''加拿大航空624號班機'''（AC624/ACA624）是一架由[[多倫多|多倫多]]飛往[[哈利法克斯|哈利法克斯]]的定期航班<ref name=CBCNews-2015-03-29-1.3013979>{{cite news |url= http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/nova-scotia/air-canada-ac624-touched-down-335-metres-short-of-runway-tsb-says-1.3013979 |title= Air Canada AC624 touched down 335 metres short of runway, TSB says |date= 2015-03-29 |publisher= CBC News |accessdate= 2016-02-20 |archive-date= 2015-04-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150402115614/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/nova-scotia/air-canada-ac624-touched-down-335-metres-short-of-runway-tsb-says-1.3013979 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name=airportia-ac624>{{cite web |url= http://www.airportia.com/flights/ac624/toronto/halifax/ |title= Air Canada Flight AC624: Toronto to Halifax – AC624 Air Canada Flight |accessdate= 2015-03-29 |publisher= Airportia.com |archive-date= 2015-04-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150402154322/http://www.airportia.com/flights/ac624/toronto/halifax/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name=flightradar24-cftjp>{{cite web |url= http://www.flightradar24.com/data/airplanes/c-ftjp/ |title= Full flight information and flight history for Air Canada aircraft C-FTJP |publisher= Flightradar24 AB |accessdate= 2015-03-29 |archive-date= 2015-04-01 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150401013716/http://www.flightradar24.com/data/airplanes/c-ftjp |dead-url= no }}</ref>，2015年3月29日3时43分，這架空中巴士A320由于機場附近下大雪導致的低能見度過早觸地，受损嚴重。這起事故造成[[哈利法克斯罗伯特·洛恩·斯坦菲尔德国际机场|哈利法克斯罗伯特·洛恩·斯坦菲尔德国际机场]]停電并關閉了一段時間。這起事故造成23人受傷。

2015年4月2日，[[加拿大航空|加拿大航空]]公司向每位乘客赔偿了5000加元。<ref>[http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/nova-scotia/air-canada-flight-624-passengers-receiving-5k-cheques-from-airline-1.3020040 Air Canada Flight 624 passengers receiving $5K cheques from airline; Lawyer Ray Wagner calls it 'a gratuity' and says $5K payments don't change airline's liability] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/nova-scotia/air-canada-flight-624-passengers-receiving-5k-cheques-from-airline-1.3020040 |date=20161201033830 }}, CBC News, April 2, 2015.</ref>但一集體訴訟案就因此事件被提出。

==事發過程==
加拿大航空624號班機，由[[多倫多皮爾遜國際機場|多倫多皮爾遜國際機場]]，飛往[[哈利法克斯罗伯特·洛恩·斯坦菲尔德国际机场|哈利法克斯罗伯特·洛恩·斯坦菲尔德国际机场]]。這架载有133名乘客與5名機組人員的飞机，撞擊到05號跑道的起始位置<ref name=AH/>，並撞斷了[[儀器著陸系統|儀器著陸系統]]的天線，造成起落架脱落。在撞击过程中将一根電線撞断，機場因此停電90分鐘<ref name="cbc"/>，接著，飛機以機腹滑上跑道。<ref name=AH/>

這架飛機的機翼、尾翼、起落架和左侧发动机受損，其中起落架和左发受损严重。23名乘客送至醫院，無生命危險<ref name=AH>{{cite web | url=http://avherald.com/h?article=483e7337&opt=0 | title=Accident: Air Canada A320 at Halifax on Mar 29th 2015, touched down short of runway | work=The Aviaton Herald | date=2015-03-29 | accessdate=2015-03-29 | first=Hradecky | last=Simon | archive-date=2019-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190924213405/http://avherald.com/h?article=483e7337&opt=0 }}</ref>，機長和副機長皆被送至醫院<ref name="Global">{{cite news| url=http://globalnews.ca/news/1909898/breaking-air-canada-plane-hard-landing-on-runway-at-halifax-airport/| title=Air Canada Flight 624 crashes into power line upon landing in Halifax| website=[[Global_News|Global News]]| publisher=[[Shaw_Media|Shaw Media]]| date=2015-03-29| accessdate=2015-03-29| archive-date=2015-03-29| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150329174417/http://globalnews.ca/news/1909898/breaking-air-canada-plane-hard-landing-on-runway-at-halifax-airport/| dead-url=no}}</ref>。事故發生時，天氣為[[暴風雨|暴風雨]]。机场停電有可能是因为飞机滑上到跑道前撞斷电線导致的<ref name="Independent">{{cite news| url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/airbus-a320-air-canada-plane-crashes-on-runway-at-halifax-airport-10141625.html| title=Airbus A320 Air Canada plane crashes on runway at Halifax airport| publisher=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]| date=2015-03-29| accessdate=2015-03-29| archive-date=2015-03-30| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150330191701/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/airbus-a320-air-canada-plane-crashes-on-runway-at-halifax-airport-10141625.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。電力恢復於05时12分。<ref name="cbc">{{cite news| url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/nova-scotia/air-canada-flight-leaves-runway-in-halifax-23-sent-to-hospital-1.3013979| title=Air Canada AC624 slides off runway in Halifax, 23 sent to hospital| publisher=CBC| date=2015-03-29| accessdate=2015-03-29| archive-date=2019-01-26| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083121/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/nova-scotia/air-canada-flight-leaves-runway-in-halifax-23-sent-to-hospital-1.3013979| dead-url=no}}</ref>

當飞机撞擊跑道及其他物品后，损伤已無法修復。加拿大航空一開始稱此事故是因「重著地」導致，导致部分乘客不滿。<ref name="cbc2">{{cite news| url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/nova-scotia/air-canada-flight-624-crash-hard-landing-too-soft-a-term-1.3015457| title=Air Canada Flight 624 crash: ′Hard landing′ too soft a term?| publisher=CBC| date=2015-03-31| accessdate=2015-03-31| archive-date=2019-04-28| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190428195321/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/nova-scotia/air-canada-flight-624-crash-hard-landing-too-soft-a-term-1.3015457| dead-url=no}}</ref>

==涉事飛機==
此架飛機為一架註冊編號C-FTJP的空中巴士A320<ref>[http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/nova-scotia/ac-624-crash-macgillivray-law-to-file-class-action-lawsuit-1.3015519 AC 624 crash: MacGillivray Law to file class action lawsuit; A second lawyer, Ray Wagner, says his firm is considering a class action lawsuit as well] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/nova-scotia/ac-624-crash-macgillivray-law-to-file-class-action-lawsuit-1.3015519 |date=20150405191953 }}, CBC News, March 30, 2015.</ref>，裝載[[CFM56|CFM56-5A1]]的引擎。出廠編號233，機隊編號214。首飛在1991年7月10日，原擁有者為通用電氣資本航空服務公司，並將此飛行器出租給加拿大航空。這次事故導致飛機受損嚴重因而報廢。<ref>{{cite web|title=C-FTJP Air Canada Airbus A320-211 – cn 233|url=http://www.planespotters.net/Production_List/Airbus/A320/233,C-FTJP-Air-Canada.php|website=Planespotters.net|accessdate=2016-02-20|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402154450/http://www.planespotters.net/Production_List/Airbus/A320/233,C-FTJP-Air-Canada.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==事故調查==
[[加拿大運輸安全委員會|加拿大運輸安全委員會]]（TSB）立即開始對此事故作調查。<ref name=City>{{cite web |url=http://www.citynews.ca/2015/03/29/23-treated-in-hospital-after-air-canada-plane-slides-off-halifax-runway/ |title=23 treated in hospital after Air Canada plane slides off Halifax runway |first=Keith |last=Doucette |publisher=Citynews |accessdate=2015-03-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150329182527/http://www.citynews.ca/2015/03/29/23-treated-in-hospital-after-air-canada-plane-slides-off-halifax-runway/ |archivedate=2015-03-29 }}</ref>

TSB表示並沒有發現任何機械故障或出现維修失误<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tsb.gc.ca/eng/enquetes-investigations/aviation/2015/a15h0002/a15h0002.asp |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713045914/http://www.tsb.gc.ca/eng/enquetes-investigations/aviation/2015/a15h0002/a15h0002.asp |archive-date=2018-07-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，[[法国航空事故调查处|法国航空事故调查处]]亦參與了此次事故的調查。三位來自[[空中巴士|空中巴士]]公司的空難調查員和兩位技術顧問赴加拿大調查事故。<ref>"[http://www.bea.aero/en/enquetes/flight.ac.624/flight.ac.624.php Flight AC 624, Airbus A320, registered C-FTJP – Halifax Stanfield International Airport (Canada), 29 March 2015] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6XTZXzT8c?url=http://www.bea.aero/en/enquetes/flight.ac.624/flight.ac.624.php |date=20150402001449 |dateformat=iso }}" (). ''[[Bureau_d'Enquêtes_et_d'Analyses_pour_la_Sécurité_de_l'Aviation_Civile|Bureau d'Enquêtes et d'Analyses pour la Sécurité de l'Aviation Civile]]''. Retrieved on April 2, 2015.</ref>

